      • compareTo

        public int compareTo(XSSFRow other)
        Compares two XSSFRow objects. Two rows are equal if they belong to the same worksheet and their row indexes are equal.(比较两个XSSFLow对象。如果两行属于同一工作表并且行索引相等，则两行相等。)
        Specified by:
        compareTo in interface java.lang.Comparable<XSSFRow>(界面中的compareTo.lang.Comparable)
        Parameters:
        other - the XSSFRow to be compared.(其他-要比较的XSSFLow。)
        Returns:
        • the value 0 if the row number of this XSSFRow is equal to the row number of the argument XSSFRow
        • a value less than 0 if the row number of this this XSSFRow is numerically less than the row number of the argument XSSFRow
        • a value greater than 0 if the row number of this this XSSFRow is numerically greater than the row number of the argument XSSFRow
        (如果此XSSFLow的行号等于参数XSSFLow的行号，则为0如果此XSSFLow的行号在数字上小于参数XSSFLow的行号，则为小于0的值如果此XSSFLow的行号在数字上大于参数XSSFLow的行号，则为大于0的值)
        Throws:
        java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - if the argument row belongs to a different worksheet(java.lang. IllegalArgument例外-如果参数行属于不同的工作表)

      • createCell

        public XSSFCell createCell(int columnIndex)
        Use this to create new cells within the row and return it.

        The cell that is returned is a CellType.BLANK. The type can be changed either through calling setCellValue or setCellType.

        (使用此功能在行内创建新单元格并返回它。返回的单元格是CellTyp.BLANK。可以通过调用setCellValue或setCellType来更改类型。)
        Specified by:
        createCell in interface Row(界面行中的删除单元格)
        Parameters:
        columnIndex - - the column number this cell represents(专栏索引- -此单元格代表的列号)
        Returns:
        Cell a high level representation of the created cell.(单元格是所创建单元格的高级表示。)
        Throws:
        java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - if columnIndex < 0 or greater than 16384, the maximum number of columns supported by the SpreadsheetML format (.xlsx)(java.lang. IllegalArgumentExcept-如果stringIndex < 0或大于16384，则是GlasssheetML格式（.xlsx）支持的最大列数)

      • getLastCellNum

        public short getLastCellNum()
        Gets the index of the last cell contained in this row PLUS ONE. The result also happens to be the 1-based column number of the last cell. This value can be used as a standard upper bound when iterating over cells: 
         short minColIx = row.getFirstCellNum();
 short maxColIx = row.getLastCellNum();
 for(short colIx=minColIx; colIx<maxColIx; colIx++) {
   XSSFCell cell = row.getCell(colIx);
   if(cell == null) {
     continue;
   }
   //... do something with cell
 }
        (获取此行包含的最后一个单元格的索引PLUS ONE。结果也恰好是最后一个单元格的从1开始的列号。迭代单元格时，该值可以用作标准上限：Short minCollix = row. getFirstCellHandler（）; Short MaxCollix = row. getLastCellHandler（）; for（short colIx=minColIx; colIx)
        Specified by:
        getLastCellNum in interface Row(getLastCellButtons界面行)
        Returns:
        short representing the last logical cell in the row PLUS ONE, or -1 if the row does not contain any cells.(缩写表示行中的最后一个逻辑单元格加一，或者如果行不包含任何单元格，则为-1。)

      • copyRowFrom

        @Beta
public void copyRowFrom(Row srcRow,
                              CellCopyPolicy policy)
        Copy the cells from srcRow to this row If this row is not a blank row, this will merge the two rows, overwriting the cells in this row with the cells in srcRow If srcRow is null, overwrite cells in destination row with blank values, styles, etc per cell copy policy srcRow may be from a different sheet in the same workbook(将单元格从srcRow复制到此行如果此行不是空白行，这将合并两行，将该行中的单元格与srcRow中的单元格叠加如果srcRow为空，则使用空值、样式等覆盖目标行中的单元格每个单元格复制策略srcRow可能来自同一工作簿中的不同工作表)
        Parameters:
        srcRow - the rows to copy from(srcRow -要复制的行)
        policy - the policy to determine what gets copied(策略-确定复制内容的策略)
